Device Driver for Crypto Engine for Allwinner R8 Chipset

The Crypto Engine is one encrypt/ decrypt function accelerator suitable for a variety of applications. It supports both encryption and decryption and several modes. Besides, both CPU mode and DMA method are supported for different applications.

It features:
1. Support AES, DES, 3DES, SHA-1, MD5
2. Support ECB, CBC modes for AES/DES/3DES
3. 128-bits, 192-bits and 256-bits key size for AES
4. 160-bits hardware PRNG with 192-bits seed
5. Support 32-words RX FIFO and 32-words TX FIFO for high speed application
6. Support CPU mode and DMA mode

Status: Under Development

